item.title: Grove - GPS
item.description: This Grove - GPS module is a cost-efficient and field-programmable gadget armed with a SIM28 (u-blox 6 is the old version) and serial communication configuration. It features 22 tracking / 66 acquisition channels GPS receiver. The sensitivity of tracking and acquisition both reach up to -160dBm, making it a great choice for personal navigation projects and location services, as well as an outstanding one among products of the same price class.
